title: XL Spray Mop
description:
Extra large head gets the job done faster!
•Double sided head flips for 2X the floor coverage
•Double spray nozzle for more flor coverage
•Use one side wet, one side dry!
•Safe for use on hardwood, ceramic, and linoleum flooring
•Slim, lightweight design for easy cleaning under furniture
•Refillable 14oz bottle for greater cleaning options
•Easy push button for bottle release
•Microfiber head is machine washable
•NO batteries required
